            I declare an interest as an officer of the all-party group on non-profit-making members' clubs. I recognise, as I am sure do all hon. Members, that the gaming machine
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_81wh' title='Col. 81WH &mdash; HC Deb 13 February 2002 vol 380 c81WH' name='column_81wh' href='#column_81wh' rel='bookmark'>81WH</a>
